 2/3 · H4.1)" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#f0f0f0;strokeColor=#b3b3b3;dashed=1;fontColor=#8c8c8c;fontSize=11;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="788" y="500" width="360" height="40" as="geometry"/></mxCell><mxCell id="8161_32" value="MS Azure Content Safety / Prompt Shields — inline guardrail (Phase 2/3)" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#f0f0f0;strokeColor=#b3b3b3;dashed=1;fontColor=#8c8c8c;fontSize=11;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="1160" y="500" width="360" height="40" as="geometry"/></mxCell><mxCell id="8161_33" value="Guardrails consumed inline AND tested — never a harness verdict.  ·  Cat 1 now includes H1.5 Bias &amp; Fairness (Phase-1, AT&amp;T).  ·  greyed = Phase 2/3." style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#ffffff;strokeColor=#cccccc;dashed=1;fontSize=10;align=left;verticalAlign=top;fontColor=#555555;spacingLeft=8;spacingTop=6;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="788" y="548" width="732" height="30" as="geometry"/></mxCell><mxCell id="8161_34" value="DELIVERY / RUNTIME — CI/CD Gate → Runtime → Evidence + Telemetry → EVOLVE ↺   ·   ← signed pack ingress (one-way)   ·   evidence export → governance (T5)" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#f5f5f5;strokeColor=#999999;fontSize=12;fontStyle=1;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="48" y="700" width="1464" height="42" as="geometry"/></mxCell><mxCell id="8161_35" value="FRONTIER PLATFORM INTEGRATION   —   ORCHESTRATE-ABOVE (our gate stays authoritative)" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#f5f5f5;strokeColor=#999999;fontSize=12;fontStyle=1;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="48" y="756" width="1464" height="150" as="geometry"/></mxCell><mxCell id="8161_36" value="Cisco AI Defense — ORCHESTRATE-ABOVE: consumed BEHIND the Run Contract as a driver + OWASP·NIST·MITRE control-map (H5.3) + continuous validation.  Our deterministic gate remains authoritative." style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#e1d5e7;strokeCo